channel.title: Client Images
channel.description:
Hello. I was working with Tom's Cache Suite, trying to remove the RuneScape logo from my client.. Well.. I got the Logo removed by importing the black file as the logo.dat, also tryed importing a blank titlebox and titlebutton.. Well that part didn't go too well.. This is an image of what the login screen looks like.. *Note* It shows the loading bar.. But IT IS fully loaded.
[img]http://i38.tinypic.com/ftiolc.png[/img] Also, if you cant see the image, the link is [url=http://i38.tinypic.com/ftiolc.png]http://i38.tinypic.com/ftiolc.png[/url]
If you have any clue on how to fix this, please let me know.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: October 04, 2009, 04:48:03 pm[/size][hr]Someone please help me with this.. It's very annoying.
